Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，今天就上到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下週日是期待已久的模擬考
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家準備 OK 了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的模擬考\N能夠清楚的了解上榜機率
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據考試的成績\N也有可能更改志願
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個考試非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.69,0:02:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模擬考成績不好的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次上課我會點你出來\N回答問題的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師，沒有人會因為那種事\N而感到困擾的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人期待不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過她的課蠻容易懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模擬考就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天工作也請了假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神努力一天的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到你的自言自語了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個壞習慣得改掉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說要集中精神\N是為了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唸書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唸書？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我後天有模擬考
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想說明天打工請假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力用功個一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工要請假…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模擬考這麼難嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是能了解\N自己目前能力的重要考試
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過補習班的課業好難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本趕不上進度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明趕不上課業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工回家後卻又馬上睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以最起碼在模擬考前一天\N明天一定要專心唸書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，請好好加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，開店了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，掉出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是補習班的課本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我唸書時非常重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唸書？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唸書的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力的去學習\N自己不懂或是新的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然講起來好像很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻是件很困難的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讀書，困難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明天要好好的唸書才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以ちぃ也要為我加油打氣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:05:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，怎麼能認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得再努力一點才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1，2，3，4\Nちぃ，ちぃ，ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2，2，3，4\Nちぃ，ちぃ，ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能說是完全背熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個就先看到這裡為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是英文
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個我最不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且課本又這麼厚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，這是這次最大的難關
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃晚飯前如果能看完一半的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天應該有辦法看完整本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,respect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,respect 是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,字典，字典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，我不是在玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在找字典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔，從搬家到現在\N我好像都沒看到字典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒開過的箱子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這就可以看出\N我有多麼的刻意逃避英文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,字典，字典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，沒有，沒有，沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把字典放在家裡沒帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我到現在都沒發現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣怎麼可能學得會英文嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要考試了\N我到底在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了，就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然，字典好貴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣就能繼續唸書了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，英文也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是ちぃ第一次到書店來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡叫作書店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賣著各種書的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書的意思就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫了許多東西的紙張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如有趣或有用的東西之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫著很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,だれもいない町（沒有人的小鎮）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好貴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫冊要這麼貴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果買了這個，字典就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是字典是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模擬考…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給妳的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禮…物？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我買給ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買給ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其我來教妳各種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書裡寫著更多有用的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候要說“謝謝”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（ちぃ真的好可愛）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要親熱麻煩請付錢後再親熱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳第一次看書嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫冊這種東西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看，這裡有圖畫對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後這裡是文章
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是透過圖畫與文章說故事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，妳會看字嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個小鎮裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳看得懂字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好聰明啊，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳來讀讀看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個小鎮裡沒有任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，本須和，你有在用功嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們又在親熱了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是那樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真有閒情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還特地來激勵你的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激勵？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油！加油！本須和！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油！加油！本須和！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油！加油！考前準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，我得唸書才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我連字典都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,字典怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把字典放在家裡沒帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒辦法唸英文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我的借你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，那你怎麼唸書？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我平常都有做預習跟複習
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不需要臨時抱佛腳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，竟然故意在我面前炫耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，沒什麼，新保大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼總之，到我房裡來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,respect 的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔，就是尊敬的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這單字該怎麼用？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，這裡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是當動詞與當名詞用時的差異
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是形容詞呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然就是 respectabIe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個小鎮裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有房子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從窗子望去也能看到燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是路上卻沒有半個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從窗戶朝裡面望去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻跟“那個”在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也看了其他的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是跟“那個”在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為跟“那個”在一起很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比跟人在一起還愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家都不出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個小鎮裡沒有任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去別的小鎮看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望有人能夠發現我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果只屬於我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:15:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得只喜歡我一個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是只屬於我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與我分手的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此我還是想見到\N只屬於我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一邊這麼的想著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天仍然朝著\N空無一人的小鎮走去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我…是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我好像懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的我自己會試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ！ Go ！ Let's Go ！本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，絲茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:15:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，ちぃ，妳沒事…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從外表看來，似乎沒什麼異常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟她是一台奇怪的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說實話，我也完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼原因造成她這樣\N我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連你也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時觀察一下情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒什麼應該就沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正現在運作得很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有你在，實在幫了我一個大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別掛在心上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我回去了，加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到還蠻有難度的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳全都讀完了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺已經這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來打算在晚餐前\N讀完半本課本的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果通通都沒讀到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總是無法集中精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在才開始根本就來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英文果然還是沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒關係了，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:19:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣放棄了，對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:20:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，又有幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，麻煩一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我還能撐下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，麻煩一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從後面往前傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等要幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工，打工
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，早安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:20:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考試結果雖然不能說很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但看樣子成績應該還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都多虧有ちぃ在一旁幫我打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的謝謝妳，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等下次拿到打工的薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再買點東西給妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果只屬於我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得只喜歡我一個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是只屬於我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與我分手的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此我還是想見到\N只屬於我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一邊這麼的想著\N我今天仍然朝著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空無一人的小鎮走去…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.10,0:23:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:24:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，撞到頭了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是有一堆不做不行的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.14,0:24:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋中都塞滿了東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.27,0:24:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋塞滿？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦，不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電費，瓦斯費，水費，房租，伙食費\N還有一堆有的沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.71,0:24:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，擔心秀樹的腦袋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好像內心受到劍傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.39,0:24:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，虛弱了」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.32,0:24:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她會不會感到頭痛啊？
